          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_2_p_10"><b>Annex B – Hansard References</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>68 </num>
              <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act’s passage through Parliament.</p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="3.53in 1.1in 1.64in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Hansard Reference</b></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Commons</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>4 July 2019</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/2019-07-04/debates/CE94864F-0382-45E2-909C-66E3920928FF/BusinessWithoutDebate"><u>Vol.662 Col.1451</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>8 July 2019</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/2019-07-08/debates/A6AF2105-1AAB-4C32-8B69-6E78DE83F87C/NorthernIreland(ExecutiveFormation)Bill"><u>Vol.663 Col.59</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Committee of the Whole House</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>9 July 2019</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/2019-07-09/debates/87A66283-DF13-4CC8-9069-48974EA40346/NorthernIreland(ExecutiveFormation)Bill"><u>Vol.663 Col.161</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Report and Third Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
